Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:39.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:44.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:46.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:51.54,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:54.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:56.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:02:00.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:04.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:12.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:14.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:17.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:22.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:28.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:33.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:40.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:45.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:50.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:56.06,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:03:01.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:39.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛說愛「過於沉重」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:44.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在轉變成恨之前　把它拒絕於心門之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:46.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬物皆是如此吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:51.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是把不合時宜的事隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:54.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是冒牌貨的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:56.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在扭曲了的窘迫時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:02:00.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連本應定下約定的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:04.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會毫無察覺地擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:12.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始崩壞但曾經互相理解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:14.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其撇下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:17.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的末路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:22.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中不服　想與之對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:28.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要從當初墮落的印象中逃離開去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:33.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　就算歷經千百次也要找出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:40.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的雙眸　你手中的余溫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:45.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小聲嘟囔著「愛總是讓我遍體鱗傷…」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:50.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因畏懼堅信不疑的事而哭過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道軟弱才能變強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:56.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕堅信不疑地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:03:01.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是愛的真諦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}三個月前  拉格朗日3
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.12,0:00:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive  連接完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive  連接完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認已經連接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO各部分一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩架太陽爐均正常運轉中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.09,0:00:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  開始協調測試
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧  特瑞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive  REPAUSE解除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓撲缺陷由既定狀態向高位推移
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twin-Drive的粒子同步率
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,35  37  40  47
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,49  55  58
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破了60%
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超過80%  就能進入穩定活動領域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.35,0:00:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓撲缺陷發生不穩定因素
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twin-Drive搭載率低下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融合率也處於下降中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  所有的搭配都嘗試過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼會不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底缺什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下Exia的太陽爐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想在那些傢伙行動之前做些什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.80,0:01:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的希望  Exia的GN Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:11.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}#02  Twin-Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想做什麼  把人叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然說自己是Celestial Being…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼爾·迪蘭地曾經是Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是…Gundam Meister？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  他生前駕駛過Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生前駕駛過…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道  哥哥已經死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死於四年前的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我繼承哥哥的遺志嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你也和尼爾·迪蘭地一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想改變這個世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且有為此戰鬥的覺悟的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡存有我們的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎  如果我把這個交給保安局的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安局馬上要對歐洲卡塔隆地下指揮部進行鎮壓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是來真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡蒂·馬內金上校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛前來赴任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你的到來  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們獨立治安維持部隊A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了剷除反聯邦勢力而設立的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直隸於聯邦政府的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擊對象是持有軍事力量的非聯邦參加國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自稱卡塔隆的反政府組織
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…另一個是上校你應該很熟悉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們再次採取武力介入的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方部隊就必須與之對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輿論也會站在我方一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我十分看好與Gundam有著實戰經驗的你的才幹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在A-LAWS盡情地施展拳腳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨立治安維持部隊A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦忠實的看家狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以坐下嗎  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩麗絲中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也在A-LAWS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到徵集命令  昨天到任的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯密爾諾夫上校居然能同意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的命令是不能違背的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈·斯密爾諾夫  軍銜是少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯密爾諾夫？難道是斯密爾諾夫上校的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是他兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把AEU的作戰指揮官以及人革聯的超兵都集中起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是片桐司令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:05:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應對神速
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  返回指揮所的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始Exia太陽爐的協調測試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協調模擬中Exia和O Gundam太陽爐的聯動率應該很高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:17.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(O GUNDAM: GN-000 GN系列GUNDAM的始祖機，\N即刹那曾經看到的那台)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不實測一下是不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·修亨伯格\N把新Gundam主發動機理論與TRANS-AM一起留給了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠紙上談兵就能對200年後的科學水平進行了預測嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭載兩個太陽爐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子產量指數化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是OO的Twin-Drive系統
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送飯來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在這了  一定要吃喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  我把紅哈羅也放在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照  請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事找我們請跟紅哈羅說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數據庫也可以隨意閱覽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想把我關到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被A-LAWS盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是什麼卡塔隆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是對方也這麼想就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還想進行武力介入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是與A-LAWS戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與聯邦軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府直派的獨立部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們已以鎮壓為名進行了14次屠殺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇難者達到數萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一消息已被封鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該也領教過他們的做法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府不就是在你們的武力干預下建立起來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  才要做個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續戰鬥  又會把無辜的人牽扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不戰鬥的話  人還是會死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾恩先生  測試差不多要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他呢？刹那在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去接人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接我們的同伴去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你實在喝得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我可照顧不過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  比利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你兩年的照顧  後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  九條
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來客人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是熟人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你會把這裡告訴別人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  還可以請他一起吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾敘敍舊也好嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹…刹那…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年沒見了  皇·李·諾瑞加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  她的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動代號  皇·李·諾瑞加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的戰術預報員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來你無處可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安局的鎮壓是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  受害者呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是GIN1  請求立刻聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於事態緊急  請求直接面談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia和O Gundam的協調雖然達到了目前最高數值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍超不過70%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離穩定範圍還有10%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用TRANS-AM強制啟動的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來導致超負荷的話  最糟糕的情況就是自爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再對系統進行一次檢測
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西班牙對平民的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被判斷是Gundam Throne所為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊理由：不明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Throne？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne的機體並不在本計劃之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne還搭載了疑似GN Drive的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放射出的攻擊型粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會對人體產生影響
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影響人體？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能對左手進行再生治療
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說Gundam的光束兵器中帶有對再生細胞有害的元素
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這架機體把路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是敵人  他們是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是敵人  他們是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我帶來想要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算成立了聯邦政府  世界也絲毫沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明犧牲了這麼多人  卻沒有任何改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞的計劃毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是借酒消愁的理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經厭倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事情我做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我們還會戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果促使世界變革是我們的罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要贖罪就只能使世界再次改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避有什麼不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有你那麼堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:06.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向同步衛星軌道空間站出發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:10.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開往Grand Union的特急班機F1200…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說刹那  不要管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新的Meister會來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的…Meister？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  好遲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩…怎麼  還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有這麼像嗎  我和哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹  他是萊爾·迪蘭地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  我叫洛克恩·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯  GIN1已經與Celestial Being接觸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:46.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}卡塔隆中東支部  地下設施
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟會不會協助我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以太陽光系統輸電權為把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫使參加國對其唯命是從
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對非參加國則採取棄而不管的政策
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在聯邦這做法實在是慘無人道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且聯邦過於急迫實行統一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進而成立了直屬的治安維持部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖鎮壓反抗勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去只會導致聯邦獨裁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們應該也很清楚這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是如此就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam居然再次出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道刹那也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被拘捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==============================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  為什麼要將Celestial Being的資料告訴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這四年間  您到底是為了什麼而做的這些準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要是連這種程度的危機都無法度過的話  就沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  比起改變世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您更像是在尋求戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  只有在戰鬥的盡頭才會有世界的變革
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他們取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼  李本茲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真是不錯的情報啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是Celestial Being的原特工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要通知霍姆·片桐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經找到了搭載Gundam的那艘飛船的坐標？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來自司令總部的情報  應該無誤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是片桐司令  做事就是滴水不漏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS全機出動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在起我艦將對Gundam的宇宙船發起奇襲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD  第一第二小隊  準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉  請給我出擊的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是由我決定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就留下待機吧  哈萊維準尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳部的設定  沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD啟動  各機趕快準備出發
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急暗號通信  是從托勒密上來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王留美發來的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的位置被A-LAWS知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開Seravee出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特你和伊恩儘快完成適配作業
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人部隊接近  敵人部隊接近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥準備  戰鬥準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  要戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人部隊接近  敵人部隊接近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:45.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥準備  戰鬥準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二號彈射器  艙門已經打開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee  到達彈射軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電磁彈射器電壓從230上升到520
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體位置固定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈射時機轉交給Seravee
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解  Seravee  特瑞亞·埃德  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人編隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是A-LAWS的MS嗎
