Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是這麼回事啊
