Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  刹那  這邊還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛操作就拜託你了
